Hon. Ahmed Adamu BBK alias Sarkin Ado, the Member representing Potiskum Central constituency in the Yobe State House of Assembly, Damaturu has today assisted patients with cash. Most of the beneficiaries were patients at the isolation center of the Specialist Hospital, Potiskum suspected with Diphtheria cases. This gesture was highly appreciated by the patient relations “we are indeed grateful for the support rendered to our relatives by the Lawmaker, this is a timely response and will go a long way in easing our sufferings, especially at this critical period of economic hardships, we pray to God to reward him abundantly”. Recently, there was the emergence of a mysterious contagious killer disease in Potiskum town but the government is responding to the situation.